FT  11 SEP 92 / UK Company News: TLS Range cuts deficit to Pounds 0.08m
Losses at TLS Range, the USM-quoted vehicle rental group, were cut from
Pounds 267,000 to Pounds 77,000 pre-tax for the half year ended June 30.
Turnover was virtually static at Pounds 4.7m.
Net finance charges accounted for Pounds 543,000 (Pounds 736,000). Losses
per share emerged at 0.5p (1.58p). There is again no interim dividend.
Increased demand and improved margins achieved in the first half were not
maintained in July and August and further steps were taken to reduce
overheads.
